B-ROTOR-CENTERLOCK-HS2-220MM-ROUNDED-c-Side-297x297.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/01095634/005018176007-AM-DB-ROTOR-CENTERLOCK-HS2-220MM-ROUNDED-c-Side-800x800.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/01095634/005018176007-AM-DB-ROTOR-CENTERLOCK-HS2-220MM-ROUNDED-c-Side-120x120.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/01095634/005018176007-AM-DB-ROTOR-CENTERLOCK-HS2-220MM-ROUNDED-c-Side-768x768.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/01095634/005018176007-AM-DB-ROTOR-CENTERLOCK-HS2-220MM-ROUNDED-c-Side-125x125.jpg 125w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/01095634/005018176007-AM-DB-ROTOR-CENTERLOCK-HS2-220MM-ROUNDED-c-Side.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/01095634/005018176007-AM-DB-ROTOR-CENTERLOCK-HS2-220MM-ROUNDED-c-Side.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/01095634/005018176007-AM-DB-ROTOR-CENTERLOCK-HS2-220MM-ROUNDED-c-Side-297x297.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/01095634/005018176007-AM-DB-ROTOR-CENTERLOCK-HS2-220MM-ROUNDED-c-Side-800x800.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/01095634/005018176007-AM-DB-ROTOR-CENTERLOCK-HS2-220MM-ROUNDED-c-Side-120x120.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/01095634/005018176007-AM-DB-ROTOR-CENTERLOCK-HS2-220MM-ROUNDED-c-Side-768x768.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/01095634/005018176007-AM-DB-ROTOR-CENTERLOCK-HS2-220MM-ROUNDED-c-Side-125x125.jpg 125w\"></a></p><p>Available in Centerlock or 6-Bolt hub interfaces, both versions are offered in 160, 180, 200, and 220mm diameters, at $50, $55, $60, and $65 respectively. While both 6-Bolt and Centerlock rotors are sold for the same price, the 6-bolt rotors include the mounting bolts, but the Centerlock Rotors do&nbsp;<em>not</em> include the lockring.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.sram.com/en/sram\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>sram.com</em></a></p></section></article></main></div></div>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"efd49a5c8ddc175c4d878aba5c86b2a09c022e24dc0093f86fac758d6651c500","category":"Cycling"}